  "prompt": "Which are the best jeans bands in India?",
  "response": "India has a vibrant music scene, and several bands have made a name for themselves in the jeans/rock genre. Here are some of the most notable indie rock and alternative bands from India that often feature denim styles and rock influences:\n\n1. **Parikrama** - A legendary rock band known for their fusion of Western rock with Indian classical music. They have been influential in the Indian rock scene since the early 1990s.\n\n2. **Euphoria** - Known for their catchy tunes and engaging lyrics, Euphoria blends rock with Indian folk music, and they gained fame in the 90s.\n\n3. **Indian Ocean** - A band that mixes rock with Indian folk influences, Indian Ocean is known for their thought-provoking lyrics and unique sound.\n\n4. **The Local Train** - An indie rock band that has gained immense popularity for their relatable lyrics and engaging melodies. Their music often resonates with the youth.\n\n5. **Agnee** - A fusion band that combines rock with various Indian musical styles. They are known for their melodic tunes and powerful lyrics.\n\n6. **Yodhakaa** - An experimental rock band that focuses on creating a unique sound combining different genres.\n\n7. **Sky High** - Known for their energetic performances, Sky High blends rock with other genres and is popular in the indie scene.\n\nThese bands often wear denim and embrace a rock-inspired aesthetic, making them popular figures in the Indian music landscape. Each has a unique sound and style, contributing to the diversity of the Indian music scene.",
